I opened the bedroom door, got out of bed and I came out breathing the cool air from the balcony of the house. So comfortable it is without the love bond that often restrict me to do something I like. Freedom became the last order. But I realized I needed someone who supported me with all my heart. Hmm ..
As time went on, there was an adzan sound that seemed to add to the coolness of this heart. I took the wudlu and quickly faced Him. Only one I asked for at the time, and it was always in my prayer.

S p i r i t .
I held my hand tight, cold, like a man with no purpose in life. At that time I was only able to say like people in general.
"Please forgive me, should you follow me to ustad maybe he can guide you to close to Him so as to ease this difficult burden, because by closer to Him what can not be solved? God is closer than the veins in the neck . "
The father woke up, tried to untie the tribulations and pull me to my feet.
"Please let me know where the ustad is." Say this hairy gray hair.

T h e  S o l u t i o n .
Slowly I approached the person.
"Why are you so gloomy? What's really going on? Maybe I can help you alleviate your burden."
"I'm going through a tough thing, my business goes bankrupt and I'm left behind by my wife and son. What should I do, I do not have anyone anymore."
I was speechless because I could not feel or experience what was experienced by this Father.
Silent reflective also in empty mind I can not think how to make this person able to release this heavy burden.
I propped my body next to my father and accompanied him for a moment.
"Why do you want to accompany me son?" Said a smile that slightly inflated from his face.

D a w n .
What is a big rock pile? Covered by green trees. Sand covered the backdrop of a solid creation. But so fragile by Him. Like cotton flying here and there, it will happen.
It was really happy to hear the ustad saying at shubuh time. Cold, cool, dew, dawn slowly appeared is a daily favors that sometimes we are less grateful.
"You're there, come over here. Let off for a moment your social media play activities let's enjoy this morning." Said the parents who are doing yoga around the mosque.
I also came down from the stairs of the mosque is composed of pebbles, while saying Alhamdulillah I was given the opportunity to enjoy this shubuh atmosphere.
From afar I saw a man sitting with his head bowed. Like having a problem that seemed to close the smile the next morning.
